{"type":"message","id":"7152f5d0","parentId":"1eafa625","timestamp":"2026-03-31T16:42:34.462Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"We need to provide raw JSON patch? The gateway config.patch expects raw? Actually from description: config.patch (partial update, merges with existing). It expects a JSON patch? The error says raw required, maybe need to include raw field with the patch JSON string? Let's look at the tool definition: config.patch has parameters: action, delayMs, reason, gatewayUrl, gatewayToken, timeoutMs, path, raw, baseHash, sessionKey, note. It expects raw?: string. So we need to provide raw JSON string of the patch. Let's construct raw patch: we want to set agents.list to the array as described. So raw should be JSON string.\n\nWe'll do:\n\n{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"list\": [\n      {\"id\": \"main\", \"identity\": {\"name\": \"bbymama\", \"theme\": \"Warm, supportive, genuinely helpful\", \"emoji\": \"📈\"}, \"subagents\": {\"allowAgents\": [\"*\"]}},\n      {\"id\": \"researcher\", \"subagents\": {\"model\": \"anthropic/claude-sonnet-4\"}},\n      {\"id\": \"coder\"},\n      {\"id\": \"orchestrator\", \"subagents\": {\"allowAgents\": [\"researcher\", \"coder\"]}}\n    ]\n  }\n}\n\nNote: we should preserve other parts; but patch merges, so we can just provide that.\n\nLet's call config.patch with raw set to that JSON string.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_616a931e70184812802e5581","name":"gateway","arguments":{"action":"config.patch","path":"agents.list","raw":"{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"list\": [\n      {\n        \"id\": \"main\",\n        \"identity\": {\n          \"name\": \"bbymama\",\n          \"theme\": \"Warm, supportive, genuinely helpful\",\n          \"emoji\": \"📈\"\n        },\n        \"subagents\": {\n          \"allowAgents\": [\n            \"*\"\n          ]\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"researcher\",\n        \"subagents\": {\n          \"model\": \"anthropic/claude-sonnet-4\"\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"coder\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"orchestrator\",\n        \"subagents\": {\n          \"allowAgents\": [\n            \"researcher\",\n            \"coder\"\n          ]\n        }\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n}","note":"Updating agents list per subagent creation guidelines"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"nvidia/nemotron-3-super-120b-a12b","usage":{"input":29186,"output":549,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29735,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774975318438,"responseId":"chatcmpl-b9267d9a0e274470"}}
